Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • Card

  • public class Card
extends java.lang.Object
    Card.java A card has a suit (spade, heart, diamond, club) and a face (ace, 2, 3, ..., 10, Jack, Queen, King). This class provides methods for drawing and constructing a card.
    Version:
    Mar 15, 2014
    Author:
    Jake Wilson
